Name: Epic Wuldr Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Greater Wuldr Rune, Level 4 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes war, combat skill, and honor. Those who channel it find that their martial prowess is enhanced.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following features.SPACERunic StrikeSPACEAs an action, you can empower your next attack with runic energy. If you succeed on your next weapon attack, you can add DAMAGE3-5DAMAGEd8 radiant damage to the weapon's damage. Additionally, the target is unable to take reactions until the end of your next turn.SPACESPACEBerserker AspectSPACEAs a bonus action, you call upon the rage of warriors past. For the next TIME3-7TIME rounds, you reduce damage you take by an amount equal to twice your Wisdom modifier.SPACESPACESpoiled for a FightSPACEAs a reaction, when you roll for initiative, you can make a single melee weapon attack against a creature within reach. When you make an attack in this way, your reach extends by 5 feet. In addition, if the attack hits, you can add DAMAGE4-6DAMAGEd8 radiant damage to the weapon's damage. On its first turn in combat, the target must choose whether it gets a move, an action, or a bonus action; it gets only one of the three.SPACECall to BattleSPACEAs an action, you can utter a warcry that bolsters your allies. All creatures of your choice within DISTANCE30-45DISTANCE feet of you that can hear you gain temporary hit points equal to twice your number of Runic Attunement Slots + their Constitution modifier (minimum of 1).SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 5 runic attunement slots. Requires Constitution 17 or greater to attune.
